{"pageProps":{"bookInfo":{"id":"24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622","name":"高性能的mysql","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql","chapterList":[{"id":"24fa845e25adb12aa70795d5ab0e3058","type":"chapter","name":"01mysql 逻辑架构.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql\\01mysql 逻辑架构.md","url":"/book/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622/24fa845e25adb12aa70795d5ab0e3058"},{"id":"e7deb2976085904fdb60f28f10820220","type":"chapter","name":"02mysql 基准测试.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql\\02mysql 基准测试.md","url":"/book/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622/e7deb2976085904fdb60f28f10820220"},{"id":"54ad46cd31428b8bcb1dce519c9a1a67","type":"chapter","name":"03服务器性能剖析.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql\\03服务器性能剖析.md","url":"/book/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622/54ad46cd31428b8bcb1dce519c9a1a67"}],"title":"03服务器性能剖析","type":"book","url":"/book/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622","content":"\n    \n    \n      <div class=\"crossnote markdown-preview  \">\n      \n<h1 id=\"性能优化\">性能优化 </h1>\n<h2 id=\"简介\">简介 </h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>性能：完成某件任务所需的时间度量，即响应时间<br>\n优化：在一定的工作负载下尽可能的降低响应时间</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"性能剖析\">性能剖析 </h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>测量任务所花费的时间<br>\n对结果进行统计和排序，将重要的任务排到前面</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"性能剖析会导致服务器变慢么\">性能剖析会导致服务器变慢么？ </h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>是的 是因为性能剖析确实会导致应用慢一点<br>\n不是 是因为性能剖析可以帮助应用运行的更快<br>\n性能剖析和定期检测都会带来额外开销，问题在于这部分的开销有多少，并且由此获得收益是否能够抵消这些开销<br>\n大多数设计和构建过高性能应用程序的人相信，应该尽可能测量一切可以测量的地方，并且接受这些测量带来的额外开销，这些开销应该被当做应用程序的一部分</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"是什么导致性能低下\">是什么导致性能低下 </h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>资源被过度使用，余量已经不足以正常工作<br>\n资源没有被正确配置<br>\n资源已经损坏或者失灵</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"md-sidebar-toc\">\n<div class=\"md-toc\">\n<details style=\"padding:0;;padding-left:0px;\" open=\"\">\n        <summary class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\">\n          <a href=\"#性能优化\" class=\"md-toc-link\"><p>性能优化</p>\n</a>\n          </summary>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#简介\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>简介</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#性能剖析\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>性能剖析</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#性能剖析会导致服务器变慢么\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>性能剖析会导致服务器变慢么？</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#是什么导致性能低下\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>是什么导致性能低下</p>\n\n          </a></div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n    \n</div>\n</div>\n      <a id=\"sidebar-toc-btn\">≡</a>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n<script>\n\nvar sidebarTOCBtn = document.getElementById('sidebar-toc-btn')\nsidebarTOCBtn.addEventListener('click', function(event) {\n  event.stopPropagation()\n  if (document.body.hasAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')) {\n    document.body.removeAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')\n  } else {\n    document.body.setAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc', true)\n  }\n})\n</script>\n      \n  \n    <script>\n</script>"},"revalidate":200,"title":"03服务器性能剖析"},"__N_SSG":true}